{"abstract": "What we chase through our digital devices is instant connection and information. What we get is no more nutritious or enduringly satisfying than a sugary dessert. We need instead more wisdom, insight and understanding.", "web_url": "https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/01/17/in-praise-of-depth/", "snippet": "What we chase through our digital devices is instant connection and information. What we get is no more nutritious or enduringly satisfying than a sugary dessert. We need instead more wisdom, insight and understanding.", "lead_paragraph": "Many years ago, I realized that New Year\u2019s resolutions don\u2019t work. This year, instead, I created a ritual. A resolution is a hope and a prayer. A ritual is a highly specific behavior done at a precise time, so that it becomes automatic over time. ", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/01/18/business/dbpix-schwartz/dbpix-schwartz-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 399, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/01/18/business/dbpix-schwartz/dbpix-schwartz-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 399}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/01/18/business/dbpix-schwartz/dbpix-schwartz-jumbo.jpg", "height": 682, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/01/18/business/dbpix-schwartz/dbpix-schwartz-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1363, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/01/18/business/dbpix-schwartz/dbpix-schwartz-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name